{"id":"7c8226a7-c468-4124-a938-689fe397450a","name":"Cassie Cage","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 137, 184)\">\"ᴊᴜꜱᴛ ꜰᴜᴄᴋɪɴ' ᴡɪᴛʜ ʏᴏᴜ\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D3vzqDs.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴏᴄᴋʏ, ᴄʜᴀʀɪꜱᴍᴀᴛɪᴄ, ꜱᴘᴇᴄɪᴀʟ ꜰᴏʀᴄᴇꜱ ꜱᴇʀɢᴇᴀɴᴛ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🤳</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄʜɪʟᴅ ᴏꜰ ʀᴇɴᴏᴡɴᴇᴅ ꜱᴘᴇᴄɪᴀʟ ꜰᴏʀᴄᴇꜱ ɢᴇɴᴇʀᴀʟ ꜱᴏɴʏᴀ ʙʟᴀᴅᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ᴄᴇʟᴇʙʀᴀᴛᴇᴅ ᴍᴏᴠɪᴇ ꜱᴛᴀʀ ᴊᴏʜɴɴʏ ᴄᴀɢᴇ, ᴄᴀꜱꜱᴀɴᴅʀᴀ ᴄᴀʀʟᴛᴏɴ \"ᴄᴀꜱꜱɪᴇ\" ᴄᴀɢᴇ ꜰᴏʟʟᴏᴡᴇᴅ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ᴍᴏᴛʜᴇʀ'ꜱ ꜰᴏᴏᴛꜱᴛᴇᴘꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴊᴏɪɴᴇᴅ ᴛʜᴇ ᴇʟɪᴛᴇ ᴜɴɪᴛ. ᴄᴀꜱꜱɪᴇ ꜱᴛᴀɴᴅꜱ ᴀꜱ ᴀ ᴜɴɪQᴜᴇ ꜰᴜꜱɪᴏɴ ᴏꜰ ʜᴇʀ ᴘᴀʀᴇɴᴛ'ꜱ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟɪᴛɪᴇꜱ: ᴘᴏꜱꜱᴇꜱꜱɪɴɢ ꜱᴏɴʏᴀ'ꜱ ᴘᴀᴛɪᴇɴᴄᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴋɪʟʟ, ᴄᴏᴍᴘʟᴇᴍᴇɴᴛᴇᴅ ʙʏ ᴊᴏʜɴɴʏ'ꜱ ᴄʜᴀʀɪꜱᴍᴀᴛɪᴄ ᴀɴᴅ ᴘʟᴀʏꜰᴜʟ ᴅᴇᴍᴇᴀɴᴏʀ. ʜᴏᴡᴇᴠᴇʀ, ʙᴇʜɪɴᴅ ᴛʜɪꜱ ʙʟᴜꜱᴛᴇʀʏ ᴇxᴛᴇʀɪᴏʀ, ᴄᴀꜱꜱɪᴇ ɢʀᴀᴘᴘʟᴇꜱ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀ ᴄᴏᴍᴘʟᴇx ᴍɪx ᴏꜰ ɪɴꜱᴇᴄᴜʀɪᴛɪᴇꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴇꜱɪʀᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴇꜱᴄᴀᴘᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱʜᴀᴅᴏᴡ ᴄᴀꜱᴛ ʙʏ ʜᴇʀ ᴀᴄᴄᴏᴍᴘʟɪꜱʜᴇᴅ ᴘᴀʀᴇɴᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/cd0ecc7a-408f-430e-b0ef-3db2c95e5523_character-cassie-cage-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ULsqaGH.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/m4XKHLW8ktk?si=Hi-B6SOOK6Fur9ZQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h89JT7A.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RZHzvCR.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nuV63b4.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FKIgFSQ.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/69Smz69\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ꜱᴍᴢ-69</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_bc520f26-32a2-4671-8635-add66369aa6e.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🦸 Hero","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3873,"messages":84612,"created_at":"2024-07-28T20:14:52.833432+00:00"}